# shadcn/ui Components

This project uses **shadcn/ui** for UI components, not direct Radix UI imports.

## Installation:
- Use `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component>` to install components
- Components are installed to [components/ui/](mdc:components/ui/)
- Configuration is in [components.json](mdc:components.json)

## Available Components:
- `tabs` - Already installed in [components/ui/tabs.tsx](mdc:components/ui/tabs.tsx)
- `button` - Already installed
- `card` - Already installed
- `input` - Already installed
- `textarea` - Already installed
- `avatar` - Already installed

## Usage:
```tsx
import { Tabs, TabsList, TabsTrigger, TabsContent } from "@/components/ui/tabs"
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from "@/components/ui/card"
```

## Important:
- Never import directly from `@radix-ui/*` packages
- Always use the shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/`
- After installing new components, remove any conflicting direct Radix UI dependencies
